title: Windows 10 x64 Enterprise LTSB MULTi-13 April 2016 {Generation2}
description:
* Windows 10 x64 Enterprise 2015 LTSB MULTi-13 April 2016 {Generation2}


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and twelve executable svf-files.

* All exe-files are created from original MSDN releases. 

* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source)
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.

* Screenshots:
[url]http://extraimago.com/image/aSFf[/url]

* Hashes & sources attached in a separate .txt

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language

* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO

* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ORIGINAL ISO in the selected language.

[ CONTENTS ]

[ SOURCE ISO ]

* W10.LTSB.X64.en-US.iso - 4,24GB

* Integrated / Pre-installed:

* KB3116097
* KB3118714
* KB3119598
* KB3120830
* KB3122962
* KB3141032
* KB3122962
* KB3144756
* KB3147457

* Setupcomplete / Post-install:

* .NET Framework 3.5
* KB890830
* Defender Updates
 
[ FEATURES ]

* UEFI-ready 
* (Use attached Rufus USB-tool to make UEFI-bootable).
* Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset 10.0 (Microsoft DaRT)

* Windows 10 Enterprise 2015 LTSB
* Windows 10 Enterprise 2015 LTSB - KMS

* KMS = Activation by KMS
 (Exclusions made in Defender)

* Screenshots:
[url]http://extraimago.com/image/aSH8[/url]
